messages.message: @pauline.comising this error is coming from the backend - it's looking for a metadata.json file in `load_snapshot_metadata_file` and it doesn't exist.

Hey! ah yes I see these accuracy runs were created a week or so ago, and we made a bug fix that causes older gt set snapshots to fail (though the ground truth set itself should still be fine). Can you re-run your accuracy test to see if the snapshot still fails to load?
